def extract_time(time_str):
    """
    Extract time from file name
    """
    start = time_str.find('-')
    end = time_str.find('.csv')
    time_str = time_str[start + 1:end]
    time = time_str.split('_')
    y, m, d, h, mi = time
    return y, m, d, h, mi
In [3]:
def csv_creater(path):
    """
    Create a pandas Dataframe with format: row - username, column - update time

    type path: String. path which stores original csv files.
    """
    files = os.listdir(path)
    names_set = set()
    output_df = pd.DataFrame()
    for f in files:
        yy, mm, dd, hh, mi = extract_time(f)
        cur_time = yy + '-' + mm + '-' + dd + ' ' + hh + ':' + mi
        # create a new column for new time
        output_df[cur_time] = 0
        df = pd.read_csv(path + '/' + f)
        existed_names = output_df.index.values
        for row in df.iterrows():
            name = row[1]["name"]
            vote = int(row[1]["vote"])
            if name not in existed_names:
                # if it is a new person, create a new row
                output_df.loc[name] = 0
            # else locate and write
            output_df.loc[name, cur_time] = vote
    return output_df

def plot_data(pd_frame, show = False, show_num = 9, step = 1, save_to = None):
    """
    :type pd_frame: Pandas Dataframe from csv_creater
    :type show: bool, show number of votes or not
    :type show_num: int, how many user will be shown in the figure(not exceed len(pd_frame))
    :type step: int
    :type save_to: None or String, if it is a string, it should be a path+filename to export result figure
    """
    # 解决中文乱码问题
    plt.rcParams['font.sans-serif']=['SimHei']
    # figure size
    plt.figure(figsize=(max(20, len(pd_frame.iloc[0])//step//3), 10))
    names = pd_frame.index.values.tolist()
    x = pd_frame.columns.values.tolist()[::step]
    l = min(show_num, len(pd_frame))
    for i in range(l):
        y = pd_frame[i:i + 1].values[0][::step]
        plt.plot(x, y, label = names[i])
        # data label
        if show == True:
            for a, b in zip(x, y):
                plt.text(a, b, b, ha='center', va='bottom', fontsize=5)
    plt.title("2021微博之夜投票总票数")
    plt.xlabel('时间',fontsize=10)
    plt.xticks(rotation="75", fontsize = 6)
    plt.ylabel('票数',fontsize=10)
    plt.legend(loc = "upper left")
    if save_to:
        plt.savefig(save_to)
    plt.show()

def plot_inc_rate(pd_frame, show = False, show_num = 9, step = 1, rm_noice = True, save_to = None):
    """
    :type pd_frame: Pandas Dataframe from csv_creater
    :type show: bool, show number of votes or not
    :type show_num: int, how many user will be shown in the figure(not exceed len(pd_frame))
    :type step: int
    :type save_to: None or String, if it is a string, it should be a path+filename to export result figure
    """
    # 解决中文乱码问题
    plt.rcParams['font.sans-serif']=['SimHei']
    # figure size
    plt.figure(figsize=(max(25, len(pd_frame.iloc[0])//step//7), 7))
    names = pd_frame.index.values.tolist()[:show_num]
    x = pd_frame.columns.values.tolist()[::step][1:]
    l = min(show_num, len(pd_frame))
    for i in range(l):
        y = pd_frame[i:i + 1].values[0][::step]
        y_rate = []
        for j in range(1, len(y)):
            if y[j-1] and y[j]:
                rate = y[j] - y[j - 1]
                if rm_noice:
                    if j > 1:
                        pre = y[j - 1] - y[j - 2]
                    if rate > 100000 and rate > 3 * pre:
                        rate -= 100000
                y_rate.append(rate)
            else:
                y_rate.append(0)
        plt.plot(x, y_rate, label = names[i])
        # data label
        if show:
            for a, b in zip(x, y_rate):
                plt.text(a, b, b, ha='center', va='bottom', fontsize=5)
    plt.title("2021微博之夜每" + str(step * 20) + "分钟票数增长量")
    plt.xlabel('时间',fontsize=10)
    plt.xticks(rotation="75", fontsize = 6)
    plt.ylabel('票数',fontsize=10)

    plt.legend(loc = "upper left")
    if save_to:
        plt.savefig(save_to)
    plt.show()
In [8]:
def draw_increase_df(pd_frame, step = 1):
    """
    :type pd_frame: Pandas DataFrame return from def csv_creator
    :type step: int
    :rtype df: Pandas Dataframe, increase in every step * 20 minutes
    """
    names = pd_frame.index.values.tolist()
    times = pd_frame.columns.values.tolist()
    df = pd.DataFrame(data = 0, columns=times[1::step], index = names) 
    for name in names:
        for i in range(1, len(times)):
            df.loc[name, times[i]] = pd_frame.loc[name, times[i]] - pd_frame.loc[name, times[i - 1]]
    return df

def abnormal_data(dt, step = 1):
    times = dt.columns.values.tolist()
    for i in range(len(dt)):
        curseries = dt.iloc[i]
        name = curseries.name
        for j in range(len(curseries)):
            curval = dt.iloc[i, j]
            if 0 < j < len(curseries) - 1:
                pre = dt.iloc[i, j - 1]
                addition = ""
                if j > 1 and dt.iloc[i, j - 2] == 0:
                    addition = "(之前未上榜导致增长量无法获取)"
                suf = dt.iloc[i, j + 1]
                
                if pre > 0 and suf > 0:
                    # if curval > 10000 * step:
                    #     print(name + "在" + str(20 * step) + "分钟内增长量大于" + str(step * 1) + "万的投票出现在" + times[j] + ", 数值为" + str(curval) + ", 之前同时间增长量为" + str(pre) + addition + ", 之后同时间增长量为" + str(suf))
                    # 去除粉丝群带来的噪点
                    if curval > 100000 and curval > 4 * pre:
                        curval -= 100000
                    if pre > 5 * curval and suf > 7 * curval and suf > 5000 and pre > 5000:
                        print(name + "在" + times[j] + "出现异常数据点, 表现为数据断层(一般为刷票行为), 该数据点值为" + str(curval) + ",前置数据点值为" + str(pre) + ",后续数据点值为" + str(suf))
                    elif curval > 5000 and curval > 7 * pre:
                        print(name + "在" + times[j] + "出现异常数据点, 表现为投票数异常增长, 该数据点值为" + str(curval) + ",前置数据点值为" + str(pre) + "(若为0点或早上7-9点之间出现的第一次则为正常现象,并非刷票) 其后数据点值为" + str(suf))
